sourcesContent: import { Box, Typography } from '@mui/material' import React, { useContext, useEffect } from 'react' import { UserContext } from '../../Context/Context' function view() { const { details } = useContext(UserContext) useEffect(() => { const { name, url } = details }, []) return ( Product Details Rate: name:{details.name} contact: category: type: date: ) } export default view
